@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### List portfolios
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/portfolios

### Portfolio by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/portfolios/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa

### Portfolio holdings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/portfolios/aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa/holdings

### Instruments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/instruments

### Submit performance calculation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/performance-calculations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "portfolioId": "aaaaaaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaa-aaaaaaaaaaaa",
  "startDate": "2025-01-01",
  "endDate": "2025-01-10"
}
